How did you find yourself writing an Python building platform?

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:40.600
Awesome.

00:00:40.840 --> 00:00:42.620
Yeah, I went to school for engineering.

00:00:43.190 --> 00:00:44.660
This was actually back in Canada.

